# Chrome Debug Mode Requirement

Before starting the OpenClaw gateway server, ensure Chrome is running in debug mode.

## Required Command

```bash
./start-chrome-debug.sh
```

## Startup Order

1. Run `./start-chrome-debug.sh`
2. Run onboarding/auth flow as needed (`./onboard.sh`)
3. Start gateway (`./server.sh start`)

If server/chat browser providers fail, first verify debug Chrome is active on `http://127.0.0.1:9222`.
